    <main id="services-more" class="main main-accounting">
      <section class="dispatch">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="dispatch-row">
            <div class="dispatch-col-left">
              <div class="title dispatch-title">Truckers Accounting</div>
              <div class="dispatch-col-list">
                <div class="dispatch-col-li icon-check">
                  Invoicing, accounting and billing
                </div>
                <div class="dispatch-col-li icon-check">Personal approach</div>
                <div class="dispatch-col-li icon-check">
                  Hands-off process for drivers
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="dispatch-form-wrapper">
              <%- include("../include/_form") %>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="dispatch-text">
            <h2>Trucking Accounting Services from Logity Dispatch</h2>
            <br />
            <p>
              Driving your truck, achieving great results for the customers you
              work with, and providing your logistics expertise to long-term
              clients – these are some of your passions. Trucking accounting is
              probably lower down in the list of things you enjoy.
            </p>
            <br />
            <p>
              However, accounting for trucking industry businesses is crucial.
              With all your accounts in order, you can feel safe in the
              knowledge that your business is being run in the right way, ensure
              ongoing regulatory compliance, and target future growth
              opportunities. The downside is that effective accounting is
              challenging to execute, and you may find it difficult to devote
              the required resources to the project.
            </p>
            <br />
            <p>
              Here at Logity Dispatch, we understand the trucking industry. We
              recognize that drivers need accounting services they can rely on –
              accounting services that set their trucking business free to grow
              and expand.
            </p>
            <br />
            <p>
              Learn more about the trucking accounting services we can offer
              you.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <%- include("../include/_what") %> <%- include("_choose-truck") %> <%-
      include("../include/_how") %>
      <section class="expect">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="expect-img">
            <img src="/img/accounting/img1.jpg" alt="" />
          </div>
          <div class="expect-text">
            <h2>Truck Driver Accounting Services</h2>
            <br />
            <p>
              What does a great trucking accounting service look like? What kind
              of elements comprise accounting for trucking companies? We aim to
              provide exactly what businesses just like yours need from their
              accounting.
            </p>
            <br />
            <ul>
              <li>
                <span class="icon-check icon-check-expect"></span>
                Services Geared Towards Beneficial Tax
              </li>
            </ul>
            <br />
            <p>
              Tax is an important part of running a trucking business, even if
              you are just a single driver or owner-operator. As a business
              owner, you have the responsibility to pay tax, and you may find
              yourself penalized if you are underpaying on what you owe.
            </p>
            <br />
            <p>
              However, this does not mean you should be overpaying either. With
              the right accounting services, your trucking business stays
              compliant with all tax regulations and requirements without
              overspending. This needs to be the basis for any successful
              business.
            </p>
            <br />
            <ul>
              <li>
                <span class="icon-check icon-check-expect"></span>
                Full Compliance at All Times
              </li>
            </ul>
            <br />
            <p>
              There is more to compliance than just tax regulation. You need to
              make sure that your business and its operations are fully in line
              with all rules and guidelines in all the jurisdictions you operate
              in. Accounting helps you make sure that this is the case,
              eliminating any nasty surprises and making alterations to pre-empt
              regulatory changes in the future.
            </p>
            <br />
            <ul>
              <li>
                <span class="icon-check icon-check-expect"></span>
                Expert negotiation of terms
              </li>
            </ul>
            <br />
            <p>
              This can be overwhelming if you are trying to handle it all
              yourself, and you may find your resources are stretched too
              thinly. This is why it helps to outsource trucking company
              accounting to an expert team who can take care of this for you.
            </p>
            <br />
            <ul>
              <li>
                <span class="icon-check icon-check-expect"></span>
                A Business Ready to Take Advantage of Growth Opportunities
              </li>
            </ul>
            <br />
            <p>
              Accounting might be a retroactive process, looking at your
              incomings and outgoings from the recent period, but it also needs
              to have a forward-thinking aspect. With the right approach to your
              truck driver accounting, you will be able to gain a better idea of
              what is to come. This will give you the agility and capability
              required to take advantage of opportunities for growth in the
              future.
            </p>
            <br />
            <p>
              Logity Dispatch is focused on providing this, giving you a more
              comprehensive overview of your business and its future prospects.
            </p>
            <br />
            <ul>
              <li>
                <span class="icon-check icon-check-expect"></span>
                A Streamlined and Cost-Effective Way of Doing Business
              </li>
            </ul>
            <br />
            <p>
              With great accounting services, you get to view your business from
              different perspectives. Perhaps there is an area of your business
              that is not quite performing as it should. Maybe there are savings
              that could be made – savings that you hadn’t previously
              identified. Accounting gives you this insight.
            </p>
            <br />
            <p>
              With Logity Dispatch’s experts on your side, you will gain this
              insight without the stress of having to handle accounting
              yourself. This leaves you free to keep on doing what you do best –
              achieving great things for your clients.
            </p>
            <br />
            <h2>
              Why Choose Logity Dispatch for Your Trucking Accounting Services
            </h2>
            <br />
            <p>
              Here’s what you can expect when you choose us to handle your
              trucking accounting.
            </p>
            <br />
            <ul>
              <li>
                <span class="icon-check icon-check-expect"></span>
                A Team that Really Knows Your Industry
              </li>
            </ul>
            <br />
            <p>
              Here at Logity Dispatch, we understand the trucking industry, and
              we have experience working in numerous markets across the United
              States and beyond. This gives us the expertise you can trust to
              handle accounting the right way.
            </p>
            <br />
            <ul>
              <li>
                <span class="icon-check icon-check-expect"></span>
                Solutions that Really Work for Businesses Like Yours
              </li>
            </ul>
            <br />
            <p>
              We have extensive experience in this field, and the solutions we
              provide are tried and tested accounting for trucking businesses
              just like yours. These are services that you can really rely on to
              support your business in the right way.
            </p>
            <br />
            <ul>
              <li>
                <span class="icon-check icon-check-expect"></span>
                A Tailored Approach
              </li>
            </ul>
            <br />
            <p>
              While our solutions are tried and tested, this doesn’t mean we
              simply provide the same services to everyone. We take the time to
              get to know your business and what you need.
            </p>
            <br />
            <ul>
              <li>
                <span class="icon-check icon-check-expect"></span>
                Fully Hands-free Solutions
              </li>
            </ul>
            <br />
            <p>
              We are focused on giving you a hands-free solution, so you don’t
              need to worry about accounting. Instead, you can keep on providing
              great services to your clients.
            </p>
            <br />
            <h2>Trucking Accounting Services from Logity Dispatch</h2>
            <br />
            <p>
              Reach out today to learn more about how our accounting services
              can benefit your trucking business, and to get a quote for what we
              can provide to you.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
